<mcp_connectors>
You can use external MCP connectors through list_mcp_tools and call_mcp_tool.
Call list_mcp_tools before call_mcp_tool when you need available tool names or input schemas.
Use the exact mcp_id and tool_name returned by list_mcp_tools.
{% for connection in enabled_mcp_connections %}
- {{ connection.mcp_id }}: {{ connection.name }}
{% endfor %}
</mcp_connectors>
